  "description": "<p>Product Features</p>\n <ul>\n  <li>Convenient Storage SolutionOrganize your garden effortlessly with a hose reel that stores up to 82' of standard 5/8\" garden hose. Keep your outdoor space neat and free of tangled hoses.</li>\n  <li>Easy-to-Use SwivelFeatures a 180-degree swivel motion, allowing easy access to any corner of your yard. The smooth design makes it simple to pull out or retract the hose.</li>\n  <li>Versatile Quick Connectors Comes with two quick connectors (5/8\") for easy hose attachment and detachment. If you prefer, these connectors can be removed, and the reel can be directly connected to a standard 3/4\u201c\u201d threaded fitting.</li>\n  <li>Safe Hose StorageThe stationary design ensures your hose stays securely in place, preventing it from cluttering walkways or becoming a tripping hazard when not in use.</li>\n  <li>Durable and Long-LastingMade with high-quality materials for long-term performance, this hose reel outlasts flimsy plastic models and cheap metal alternatives, offering reliable storage year after year.</li>\n  <li><img src=\"https://cf.cjdropshipping.com/17394048/1889883205117677568.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" contenteditable=\"false\"/><img src=\"https://cf.cjdropshipping.com/17394048/1889883206745067520.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" contenteditable=\"false\"/><img src=\"https://cf.cjdropshipping.com/17394048/1889883209492336640.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" contenteditable=\"false\"/><img src=\"https://cf.cjdropshipping.com/17394048/1889883211044229120.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" contenteditable=\"false\"/><img src=\"https://cf.cjdropshipping.com/17394048/1889883212206051328.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" contenteditable=\"false\"/><img src=\"https://cf.cjdropshipping.com/17394048/1889883213426593792.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" contenteditable=\"false\"/><img src=\"https://cf.cjdropshipping.com/17394048/1889883214949126144.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" contenteditable=\"false\"/><img src=